Rising Star: Whatley Kallas' W. Tucker Brown

Law360, Washington (April 11, 2016, 7:46 PM ET) -- Whatley Kallas LLP’s W. Tucker Brown is making a name for himself in the health care realm far beyond his Birmingham, Alabama, base, playing a key role in high-stakes cases like the Blue Cross Blue Shield antitrust litigation and landing among six health attorneys under 40 recognized by Law360 this year.
